Language: en

00:00:00.667 --> 00:00:03.901
♪♪

00:00:03.901 --> 00:00:06.734
IN THE MYTH
"LIFE RAFT PARACHUTE,"

00:00:06.734 --> 00:00:10.634
BUSTER FOUND OUT HOW TERMINAL
VELOCITY CAN BE.

00:00:10.634 --> 00:00:13.567
WE HAVE A WHOLE FOREARM
AND A HAND OVER HERE

00:00:13.567 --> 00:00:15.734
ON THE RAFT, OVER.

00:00:15.734 --> 00:00:17.701
BUT ON THE OPERATING TABLE,

00:00:17.701 --> 00:00:21.834
ADAM AND GRANT RESURRECT BUSTER
FROM HIS FATAL FALL.

00:00:21.834 --> 00:00:23.467
ROUND THREE.

00:00:23.467 --> 00:00:24.901
[ BELL DINGS ]

00:00:24.901 --> 00:00:27.601
AND WITH BUSTER
HAVING FAILED TO RIDE THE RAFT

00:00:27.601 --> 00:00:30.968
LIKE INDIANA JONES,
JAMIE RIGS IT AS A PARACHUTE.

00:00:30.968 --> 00:00:33.968
JUST GONNA GIVE A LITTLE EXTRA
AND LACE HIM A COUPLE OF PLACES.

00:00:33.968 --> 00:00:36.534
I'M TIRED OF BUSTER
TAKING OFF ON ME.

00:00:50.467 --> 00:00:52.067
HIS ASS IS HANGING OUT.

00:00:52.067 --> 00:00:56.567
WOW. LOOK AT THAT.

00:00:56.567 --> 00:00:58.434
IT'S GOT TO WORK THIS TIME.

00:00:58.434 --> 00:01:01.167
[ LAUGHS ]
FAMOUS LAST WORDS.

00:01:01.167 --> 00:01:02.934
TORY: Looking good so far,
Steve.

00:01:02.934 --> 00:01:06.133
HE IS TAKING HIS TIME
SO HE DOESN'T RIP THE THING.

00:01:06.133 --> 00:01:10.234
HE'S GONNA FAVOR THE UPWIND SIDE
OF THE "X" A LITTLE BIT, OVER.

00:01:10.234 --> 00:01:13.534
YOU GUYS MAKE SURE
YOU CAN GET UNDER THAT TRUCK

00:01:13.534 --> 00:01:16.334
IN A HURRY, OVER.

00:01:16.334 --> 00:01:19.334
OKAY, STEVE, I'D SAY GO AHEAD
AND RELEASE AT WILL.

00:01:19.334 --> 00:01:21.000
YOU LOOK GOOD, OVER.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.767
OKAY, HE'S RELEASING, GUYS.

00:01:24.767 --> 00:01:26.734
IT'S GOING.

00:01:26.734 --> 00:01:28.234
IT'S GOING.

00:01:28.234 --> 00:01:29.968
OH, IT'S BEAUTIFUL!

00:01:29.968 --> 00:01:34.033
BE CAREFUL BEFORE YOU
SPEAK TOO SOON.

00:01:34.033 --> 00:01:37.100
LOOK AT THAT! WHOO!

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:38.868
IT'S NOT OVER YET.

00:01:38.868 --> 00:01:41.067
I KNOW.

00:01:41.067 --> 00:01:42.767
COME ON, BUSTER!

00:01:42.767 --> 00:01:46.133
LOOK AT -- THOSE LITTLE ENTRY
RAMPS ARE LIKE WINGS, YOU KNOW?

00:01:46.133 --> 00:01:47.834
OH, THAT'S GREAT!

00:01:47.834 --> 00:01:53.367
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:01:53.367 --> 00:01:56.067
Buster's on the ground.
Buster's on the ground.

00:01:56.067 --> 00:01:58.300
WELL, THAT LOOKED LIKE
A MUCH NICER RIDE.

00:01:58.300 --> 00:02:00.334
I'LL HAZARD A GUESS

00:02:00.334 --> 00:02:03.367
THAT BUSTER MAY WELL BE
INTACT THIS TIME, ENTIRELY.

00:02:03.367 --> 00:02:06.133
Narrator: BUT APPEARANCES
CAN BE DECEPTIVE.

00:02:06.133 --> 00:02:09.467
BUSTER HAS ONCE AGAIN SUSTAINED
SOME SEVERE DAMAGE.

00:02:09.467 --> 00:02:11.334
BUT WOULD HE HAVE SURVIVED?

00:02:11.334 --> 00:02:14.300
ALL THE 50-G SHOCK WATCHES BROKE
ON ALL OF HIS LIMBS,

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:17.634
BUT IN HIS CHEST, THE 75
AND THE 100 DID NOT GET TRIPPED.

00:02:17.634 --> 00:02:20.701
SO THAT MEANS THAT HE GOT
ALL BUSTED UP.

00:02:20.701 --> 00:02:24.267
HE WOULD NOT BE A HAPPY CAMPER,
BUT HE MIGHT JUST BE ALIVE.

00:02:24.267 --> 00:02:28.501
IF YOU COULD HAVE LEAPED OUT
OF THE AIRPLANE WITH THIS RAFT,

00:02:28.501 --> 00:02:30.067
INFLATED IT IN MID-AIR,

00:02:30.067 --> 00:02:32.467
RIGGED FOUR POINTS TO IT
SO YOU COULD HANG FROM IT

00:02:32.467 --> 00:02:36.701
LIKE A PARACHUTE, YOU MIGHT...

00:02:36.701 --> 00:02:38.300
JUST MIGHT SURVIVE.

00:02:38.300 --> 00:02:41.334
BUT ALL THE OTHER ASPECTS
OF THIS ARE SO UNREALISTIC,

00:02:41.334 --> 00:02:44.567
THE ODDS OF YOU BEING ABLE
TO ACHIEVE THIS RIG

00:02:44.567 --> 00:02:46.567
WHILE FALLING OUT OF A PLANE

00:02:46.567 --> 00:02:49.133
ARE SO UNLIKELY
AS TO BE ALMOST LUDICROUS.

